{"tid":2403642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男學生被控「721事件」8個月阻差辦公 罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T14:13:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c1efb3a554ab6426a405381f5fb0c61088e22424","tid":2403642,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13639&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2e8eb3b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13639</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#梁雅忻裁判官 #裁決<br />\n👤李(17) #20200322元朗 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員 <br />\n李手足被控於2020年3月22日凌晨00:40，在元朗合益路與又新街交界，故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警員24004 李文軒 (伸手攔住警員追捕2名年輕女子)<br />\n<br />\n✌️罪名不成立✌️<br />\n不批准辯方訟費申請<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n本案關鍵在於控方證人是否肯定伸手攔住牠的人是被告。根據證供，當時現場有不少人、環境混亂，而且有人跑過。警員亦沒有解釋為何截停被告，而且牠的注意力應該集中在追截的2名女子，對出手攔警之人的觀察未必可靠，難以確定該人就是被告&hellip;&hellip;詳情後補<br />\n<br />\n🟢未能舉證至毫無合理疑點，罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n梁官認為被告可以有其他離開的路線選擇，毋須冒險在混亂現場逗留，拒絕辯方訟費申請。"},{"pid":"44170c5f063a3b80ae158f0ec62b68b3002d3af3","tid":2403642,"uid":184261,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"今日3單都唔批訟費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215dc5679b0d3b2bb208cd336333660d30726148","tid":2403642,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44170c5f063a3b80ae158f0ec62b68b3002d3af3","tid":2403642,"uid":184261,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"今日3單都唔批訟費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" clas